column5: Going out to Mr. Greek for supper tonite. Our friends Hans and Gerda are coming. They'll be paying so I guess we'll really splurge!!!
I'm sure Hans and Gerda are Fed up with Greek....
Watch the bill, you may be bailing them out!
None in my area, but it looks good! Have fun!

Every time that we have an early flight out of TO; we stay the night before at the Carlingview Hotel and have supper at Mr. Geek. Oh man I can't get enough of their "Grilled Chicken & Garlic Shrimp Paros". Mouth's watering now; thanks for making me look at their menu. LOL  Dan.
